==Strategy==
{{Main|Brutus/Strategies}}

Aside from a basic melee attack that can be negated through the use of the [[Protect from Melee]] prayer, Brutus uses two special attacks, both of which give players a few [[ticks]] to move out of the way.

Additionally, Brutus cannot be [[Flinching|flinched]], but he can be temporarily [[safespot]]ted on nearby scenery objects (such as plants or with the nearby warning sign or troughs). After a short while of being safespotted, Brutus can either charge towards the player through obstacles, or move around them to reach the player.

